  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Red Dead: Reusable Sanitary Pads For Malawi Girls</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will tackle the problem of menstrual health hygiene and in part of youth unemployment. Most school girls in Malawi come from poor families. They can&apos;t afford pads and end up missing classes. Our one-year program will recruit 10 volunteers.These female volunteers will be trained to train 2400 girls in Blantyre to make reusable sanitary pads usable for 3 years and train 600 girls to make art, jewelry or sandals for sale.7,200 pads made by the trainees will be given to 7,200 poor girls</narrative>
  </description>
